\section*{Exercise 3a}

De gegeven grammatica is:

\[
\begin{array}{lll}
S &\rightarrow& NP\ VP\\
NP &\rightarrow& D\ N\\
NP &\rightarrow& PN\\
VP &\rightarrow& V\ NP\\
D &\rightarrow& a \mid all\\
N &\rightarrow& song \mid musicians\\
PN &\rightarrow& John\\
V &\rightarrow& plays \mid love
\end{array}
\]

We breiden deze grammatica uit met semantic attachments.

\subsection*{Syntactische regels}

\[
\begin{array}{lll}
S \rightarrow NP\ VP
&\qquad&
\sem{S}=\sem{NP}\app\sem{VP}\\[0.8em]
NP \rightarrow D\ N
&\qquad&
\sem{NP}=\sem{D}\app\sem{N}\\[0.8em]
NP \rightarrow PN
&\qquad&
\sem{NP}=\sem{PN}\\[0.8em]
VP \rightarrow V\ NP
&\qquad&
\sem{VP}=\sem{V}\app\sem{NP}
\end{array}
\]

\subsection*{Lexicale regels}

\[
\begin{array}{lll}
D \rightarrow a
&\qquad&
\sem{D}=\lam{P}\lam{Q}\exists x(P\app x \land Q\app x)\\[0.8em]
D \rightarrow all
&\qquad&
\sem{D}=\lam{P}\lam{Q}\forall x(P\app x \rightarrow Q\app x)\\[0.8em]
N \rightarrow song
&\qquad&
\sem{N}=\lam{x}Song(x)\\[0.8em]
N \rightarrow musicians
&\qquad&
\sem{N}=\lam{x}Musician(x)\\[0.8em]
PN \rightarrow John
&\qquad&
\sem{PN}=\lam{Q}(Q\app j)\\[0.8em]
V \rightarrow plays
&\qquad&
\sem{V}=\lam{O}\lam{z}O\app(\lam{y}Play(z,y))\\[0.8em]
V \rightarrow love
&\qquad&
\sem{V}=\lam{O}\lam{z}O\app(\lam{y}Love(z,y))
\end{array}
\]

